The molecular formula for 2-but-2-en-2-yl-9-phosphabicyclo[3.3.1]nonane is C12H21P.

- 21 hydrogen atoms (H)
- 1 phosphorus atom (P)

12 + 21 + 1 = 34 atoms. 

So, there are 34 atoms in 2-but-2-en-2-yl-9-phosphabicyclo[3.3.1]nonane.
